{"tid":638921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中興問農婦道：「菜無芯可活， 中興無芯可活否？」","createTime":"2018-04-23T06:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T06:42:24.000Z","uid":22876,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b68ad1a32857bf2bd1823e23c350542abc2f88d8","tid":638921,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"歷史上有名的當奴侵&mdash;&mdash;「紅顏禍水」之一的千年狐狸精，蠱惑美國議會不理朝政、沉迷聲色、建造酒池肉林，導致盜賊橫行、烽煙四起，世局動盪。中興多次進諫，但忠言逆耳，美國議會並不採納，老當耳旁風。<br />\n<br />\n這事兒惹惱了當奴侵，於是日日在美國議會面前進讒言，要中興挖芯以示忠誠。中興被逼無奈，只得一死以報君王。<br />\n<br />\n傳說，中興臨死前，華為給了他一道符，教他挖芯之後，將符貼在胸口，立即策馬狂奔，離開京城兩千里，只要不回頭，即使無芯也可以不死。<br />\n<br />\n中興依照吩咐行事，不想，中途遇到一名街市婆，在他身後沿街叫賣「無芯菜」，中興好奇回頭一瞅，立刻墜馬而亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/141051_9a871d5485304b28470dacec69c08c71.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F141051_9a871d5485304b28470dacec69c08c71.PNG&h=c00b2a95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54edef5194604bc99ce48aa0c8b36788ac6ead90","tid":638921,"uid":22876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:19:11.000Z","msg":"救救中興"},{"pid":"2957db43bf19100c57c85aaa54df84c3f49be8c5","tid":638921,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9601e5dc33a93e1bbe034f3a555e1aa69f5de5","tid":638921,"uid":174601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  文筆唔掂<br />\n<br />\n左抄右抄咁"},{"pid":"b13146b83ffa76b8f37b99ebfb7524d7e992774b","tid":638921,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b9601e5dc33a93e1bbe034f3a555e1aa69f5de5","tid":638921,"uid":174601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  文筆唔掂<br />\n<br />\n左抄右抄咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"體諒下"},{"pid":"5ca87509139b5fc357a733310cffa3328736f01d","tid":638921,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"細個睇果陣得呢一幕好ON9。佢唔撚問，一於等到臨老死果日先問唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}